    Golems will follow you wherever you go and will absorb
attacks until they die. You may command only one Golem at a time.

Golems which can be created:
  - clay        level 1     (costs 20  sp)
  - bronze      level 6     (costs 30  sp)
  - iron        level 11    (costs 50  sp)
  - steel       level 16    (costs 80  sp)
  - stone       level 21    (costs 120 sp)
  - diamond     level 26    (costs 200 sp)

Commands:
  - create <type>: Makes the Golem
  - destroy golem: Destroys your Golem (costs 25 sp)
